# Feather PDF — MIME conversion for the virtual printer.
# The printer's *cupsFilter wants application/vnd.cups-pdf; CUPS already knows
# how to turn any printable input into application/pdf, so this last hop just
# runs pdftopdf (which applies copies, page ranges, N-up) and hands the result
# to our backend.
#
#   source-type           destination-type          cost  filter
application/pdf            application/vnd.cups-pdf   33    pdftopdf
